I was already using a similar pump but powered by a slightly larger power supply. This surprised me in a positive way. It's really small but very high-performance. I use it to inflate two mattresses and I must say that it does its job very well and quickly. The noise level is similar if not less than the other one. In just a few minutes it inflates a mattress to the right pressure. After three inflations the charge indicator was at about 3/4ths. It contains three nozzles of different sizes and a cable (actually a little short) for charging. In short, only positive things at the moment. Recommended.

column2: Considering the size, are we sure it's a good air pump?! Bha... Let's try it! Guys, it's super! What can I say..... Useful small and therefore handy and portable, tidy and accessorised in a comfortable handbag with compartments for various accessories. The choice of 4 LEDs that indicate the level of charge is very nice. It is easily rechargeable via USB using a power bank. Or via a normal 12W socket. It has the function of inflating and deflating and is very useful if you want to use it on large inflatable objects. And the most important thing to know about the object itself given its size is the power which did not disappoint me at all. It inflated my inflatables without any effort. I recommend it and I even bought 2 of the same ones to use at home and at sea. A piece of advice: (since it is a lithium battery, if you have to use it it is preferable to recharge it to the maximum to have a longer life, but if you have to use it rarely I recommend leaving it with a half charge) overall you deserve 5 stars!

A helper for cleaning the house. All you need to do is map the house once and then you can choose the rooms to clean via the app. Bought for the upper floor since I already have another robot for the lower floor. The robot has multiple suction levels, the average one tends to be the best in terms of autonomy and it sucks well without leaving anything after finishing its work, it empties all the dust in the emptying box automatically. Equipped with a floor cleaning cloth, it allows you to wash the floor without adding detergent or my personal advice after more than a month of use is to add just a drop of detergent, no more, so as to wash diligently without leaving streaks on the floor. I admire the technology that this robot has, it has all the comforts that a robot can have, I really consider it a satisfactory purchase.

Definitely the best robot vacuum cleaner I've ever purchased. Let me start by saying that I am a fan of electronic and smart accessories and this is the 3 robot vacuum cleaners that I buy every time trying to find something better. I was very very happy, the only flaw of my old robots was having to continually empty the dust box so as not to clog up the robot and this compromised many of the automatic cleanings organized during the week. Thanks to its HUGE charging station, this robot has the ability to suck dust directly from the robot thanks to the special autonomous vacuum cleaner and fills the bag like a traditional old school vacuum cleaner. Obviously it allows you to empty the dirt much more sporadically than the collection boxes found inside the robots themselves. The assortment of accessories and spare parts supplied is also excellent (ps. there are also many spare bags). The smart interface of the robot is very advanced. Alexa App etc.. you can clearly see that it is top of the range type. Finally, I would like to talk about its cleaning characteristics. The robot is very silent but has excellent suction power. It is also really intelligent and able to understand when it is on carpets or in areas of the house that are forbidden to it. Definitely the best cleaning robot ever purchased. I recommend spending a little more and buying these products rather than perhaps having to change them after less than a year because they are unsatisfactory.

The projector offers good performance and combines good image quality with excellent audio quality. On the back there is a convenient knob to adjust the angle to avoid ugly image distortions. I purchased this impact wrench in anticipation of some work I have to do at home and I opted for this job to have power and durability. CONTENTS OF THE PACKAGE The package was delivered in an exemplary manner: the deadlines were carefully respected and the package arrived in excellent condition and without any type of dent. Furthermore, the screwdriver case is well made. Inside the package delivered by the courier we can immediately find the product packaging which contains: 1. The protective case 2. The screwdriver 3. The battery charger 4. A battery 5. 3 bushings of different sizes 6. 1 wrench adapter EXPERIENCE OF USE The screwdriver presents itself in an admirable way: it gives a strong sensation of excellent construction quality at the mere sight but also provides excellent feedback to the touch. The battery has a long life, the charger is very convenient and has two LEDs to indicate the battery charge. The screwdriver is very strong and can unscrew the wheels of the car without major problems. CONCLUSIONS I was pleasantly surprised by this product: it meets all my power and autonomy requirements! The screwdriver is the ideal combination of quality, power saving and durability. I absolutely recommend you consider purchasing this tool! If you have made it this far, thank you for reading and I hope I have been useful to you!

Then the long duration and in line with what was declared. The sound is very clean and well balanced. Finally, the feature that I liked most was the waterproofness tested despite myself. I ended up under a water bomb while jogging and the headphones got very wet but no problem. Overall, I really liked them.

I've been stranded two or three times this year with the battery flat. We have an old car that we use sporadically and maybe some lights that stay on or something in the electronics or that satellite that the insurance companies install for you, the fact is that the battery runs out if we don't use it for a while. The last time it happened, rather than do the usual thing again, that is, call and wait for the electrician to spend 40 euros, I decided to try this starter. In the worst case scenario, I thought I'd get a super power bank to charge my cell phones. And instead I was pleasantly surprised also because this gadget is really small and I never expected it to be able to start our old 2000 displacement diesel. It works very simply, the powerbank arrives, the two cables to connect to the battery with the relative red and black terminals, the cable to recharge the powerbank, instructions (few but clear). Connect the clamps to the battery poles (or to the points indicated in the car manual), start the powerbank and turn it on... that's all. Easy and easy and the fear of being stranded went away with the good grace of my husband who always had to intervene. Also very useful is the fact that the starter has an LED on one side which allows it to be used as a torch in case of need. Just one precaution: it must be charged to the maximum to work well initially with 3 dots of charge, it struggled with 5 and it started immediately. In any case, an indispensable object in a car!

I purchased this battery for my Dyson 8. The replacement was super easy and quick and the battery fit perfectly. It arrived already charged so I used it immediately. I noticed that compared to the old battery it has a higher amperage so it lasts longer. So far it's perfect and while with the old one I managed to clean the whole house and one dot remained, with this one there are two left perhaps because it's new but I've already used it several times since it arrived. What can I say for the price paid, I also recommend it because the original costs much more and this one is also more powerful.

I would like to point out that at home, given that I am in an area where even my neighbors who have an antenna on the roof sometimes lose the signal, I have installed a satellite dish to watch satellite TV with TivuSat. I put a TV under my roof in which I connected the Tim vision to watch Tim/netflix content etc. I wanted to try this antenna to see if it was possible to see DVB TV channels. Installation is super quick, you just have to screw the stem to the base and connect the cable to the TV either directly if it's a screw or with the adapter supplied together with the USB plug to the TV. When I connected it as you can see from the photo placed on the bin after I scanned it I was surprised. You can see DVB channels and even some in HD. For now I use it by placing it on the bin or on the table and so far it hasn't given me any major problems. Some channels can't be seen but the main ones can. Considering the low support I'm sure that if I had been on a raised floor everyone would be seen. However, overall I can be satisfied considering the price is not exaggerated. Do I recommend it? Certainly yes for those like me who don't have the possibility of bringing a TV cable or installing a high-cost antenna.

column2: Very useful charging station for my home office
column3: I really appreciated the USB charging station. Every day I find myself having to charge and power various electronic devices and this object has made my life easier. Very minimal and elegant object, well assembled with quality glossy plastic. Super recommended, a must have in every home!

I am very satisfied with the quality of these bluetooth headphones. I haven't had any problems pairing with my devices, stable signal and range is excellent. I used them for listening to music and for calls. The songs are reproduced with an excellent general balance, the bass in particular amazed me: there are no distortions and they are very full-bodied. Calls are also ok, no interlocutor has complained about the quality of the microphones. Excellent battery life and convenient to have the remaining battery % indicated on the case. The form factor is similar to the small and pocket-sized AirPods Pro. I recommend them.

The LEDs are strong and illuminate perfectly, guaranteeing a better range of vision. I am sure that installing LED lights is an excellent initiative to improve the safety of your car.

It has two pink straps: one more sporty and breathable, very soft and comfortable to wear, the other more elegant leather to be used with a more formal outfit. The watch allows you to monitor your daily steps by setting a goal and is very reliable. Furthermore you can monitor many other activities the interface is simple and responsive. It does not have GPS but uses the smartphone's GPS to monitor distances accurately. The watch allows you to receive a vibration when you receive a call and can also be configured to receive notifications from your smartphone. I applaud the approval for managing the smart watch: it is also very simple to use and effective. I am very satisfied with the recommended purchase.

Inconclusione is a humidifier with normal dimensions that is practical and above all economical so I recommend it to everyone. Shipping was very on time with prime. Recommended

After many negative experiences with teeth whiteners I can now say that this is the right one. The effects can already be seen after 3-4 days and in terms of price I can tell you that it is worth it. The product arrived on time and without any particular problems and inside there is a booklet that explains all the steps that need to be done, albeit in English. Highly recommended
The controller works very well. Inside the package you can find instructions in both English and Italian. Regarding the price, it may seem like a lot for a pad but I assure you that it is worth it.

Let's start with the delivery arrived on time. The box is made of cardboard with illustrations. Inside there is the deterrent, the charging cable and the mounting accessories. The rechargeable batteries are already mounted. The owl shape is very cute, time will tell if the pigeons will be afraid of it. There are two eyes with white and red flashing alarm LEDs and a piezo tweeter for ultrasound. It can be fixed with the hook or with the aluminum support divided into two pieces. The two potentiometers should be used, one to select the frequency based on the animals to be removed, the second to adjust the volume. Some frequencies are also audible to humans. Robust construction. The motion sensor lights up when charging red and turns green. Good product.

Impeccable Amazon delivery as usual. The headphones are presented in a beautiful box with an indication of the percentage of charge for each earphone and the internal battery. Remember to remove the film that protects the contacts otherwise you will not be able to charge the earphones. as soon as they were removed from the case they connected to the phone. I like how they fit the earcup. Great sound. The plastics seem to be of good quality to me. I can keep them connected even between rooms with thick brick walls. I think I can recommend purchasing one of the best ones used so far.
Easy assembly. The cable is very convenient for positioning the panel in favor of the sun and lamp where needed. Even now with little sun the lamp works regularly unlike others I have installed.

Delivery as usual impeccable. I find the cover excellent, the corner and rear protections keep the phone safe from accidental falls. Fingerprint recognition is not made difficult by the cover, in fact there is an opening where you can place your finger. For now I haven't used the film as the phone still has the original one. I can recommend this cover.

Excellent smartwatch with a very high battery life, multifunction with pedometer and sleep quality register as a gift for my son and he was happy and satisfied. The charger is very convenient to recharge it.
A great keyboard case. I gave it to my aunt who is thrilled with it! It works great, it connects on the fly.. really excellent.

Nice product, solid materials and very easy to handle. Easy to use and the different attacks can be changed easily. Different heads for the muscle groups to be stimulated. After getting intoxicated several times by putting on platelets and various chemical substances, I decided to buy this mosquito repellent lamp hoping to be able to do without everything else and so it was. The product, as shown in the photo, arrived intact, working and complete, also with instructions in Italian. column2: Excellent at home, also useful for monitoring cars in parking
column3: "A perfect microcamera for use at home. I followed the manual and it connects well to the wi fi. The application is very useful. With the motion sensor it automatically sends push notifications to phone that notifies you of the detected movement (by setting it ""max"" it even detects crazy light changes!). All the files are cataloged in the app and are automatically saved in the phone (in the gallery). Personally I used it to monitor my car in the parking lot since I found scratches made on purpose. Even though I can't use the app because the wi-fi doesn't arrive, it automatically records in a loop (files lasting 5 minutes each) as long as the battery lasts or the memory holds. I suggest a micro SD large capacity if you want it to last all night/day and a power bank. Also perfect for night vision (click the light bulb in the app). It is also very discreet. In the car everyone notices a dashcam placed in the middle of the windshield dashboard but it is much more difficult to locate this micro camera. From the photos you can see the dimensions. It resets from the app. Every time it turns on again you have to pair it by connecting to the dashcam's wi fi but it's absolutely not a problem, in fact it replaces Bluetooth making it even smarter! Highly recommended instead of spending hundreds of euros on a device that COULD detect movements in the car I solved it with this even though it was designed for the home it detects up to expectations. Excellent"

column2: Fair, functional, good value for money
column3: I received the mini camera on time, perfect and intact package. The quality is excellent (HD 1080p) and the battery lasts a long time. It also has motion detection which captures movements and activates immediately. What surprises me is the capacity it supports: up to 128GB, a lot! The SIM is not included but to my surprise a USB stick is included into which the SD card is inserted which passes the data from the camera to the PC. A plus point! In addition to the mini camera you have the two supports, a sticker, the cable with which you charge it and the booklet. Excellent for the price. Very satisfied! Also because it is discreet wherever you want to use it: internal external environments or cars.

Opening the box you will find the earphones separated and in plain sight and just below there is the charging case. Once the eartips were the right size for my ear, they remained glued there and no longer moved, they couldn't even be heard because of how comfortable they are, sometimes you forget you have them. The battery lasts a long time, it's true that I recharged it for the second time after 4 days. The touch functions are very convenient and help me carry out small operations directly from the headphones without having to use the phone

I noticed that it has a slightly larger display than other smartwatches on the market which is another plus. I bought these headphones as a gift for my cousin, well what can I say, simply fantastic, exceptional quality/price ratio. Sound test : I try the headphones with a bit of skepticism about the sound quality but as soon as I started the first song I completely changed my mind. They have a beautiful and full-bodied sound. The highs are not excessive and the mids aren't either. The bass is full-bodied, resulting in a good sound. crystal clear, not boxy" and accompanied by the enveloping body of the bass. Fully satisfied."

I bought them for my brother after he tried mine (an older model and no longer on the market). He was as happy with mine as I was. Pros: - clean and well-balanced sound on average for this price without particular unbalances on the bass (for me an excellent pro) - chaotic touch controls I only use pause and play because moving the tracks forward or even raising and lowering the volume is too cumbersome. In conclusion, I recommend the purchase to those who do not have huge demands as in the case of my brother who uses them in the gym (weight room) and to listen to music while traveling or working in front of the PC.

"I purchased these headphones because my historic wireless headphones held the battery poorly after years of honorable career. After a good week of use I can say I am very satisfied with the purchase. PRO - The thing that impressed me most I was amazed at the grip which, although it seemed a little superficial at first use, actually turned out to be extremely effective. Even when chewing or shaking the head they do not escape and do not loosen their grip by a millimetre. - The ""tail"" style airpods allow you to attach the headphones really quickly to the ear without having to press the earphone into the earcup by touching the touch controls. - The sound is crisp and clean, nothing shocking but appreciable after all the purpose of headphones like these is not the hi-fi. I didn't notice any particular engravings on any frequency which makes them very pleasant for those like me who love a neutral sound. - The digital display on the headphone holder which indicates the battery level of the box and individually when the headphones are on is very convenient. charging (but not their charge level"

column2: For iPad it is the best
column3: I tried to buy this HUB because I recently got an iPad and since I will use it a lot for work I need to connect different devices to it. There are 2 USB 3.0 ports that allow you to connect a USB stick, a mouse and a wireless keyboard at the same time (mouse and keyboard must have a common Bluetooth receiver as in my case) I can simultaneously connect the iPad to the TV (in my case it served on several occasions to illustrate photo albums to various clients) and I can download the photos and videos I take directly onto the iPad thanks to the SD and MicroSD ports. A perhaps little-recognized gem that many other HUBs don't have is the Ethernet port which allows you to connect the iPad to an even faster connection, saving connection battery by deactivating the WiFi antenna. Perhaps I won't use this function much personally thanks to the iPad's lightning-fast WiFi, but if like me you have to deal with the most disparate cases in studios and clients' homes, it is a potential lifeline that can make the difference. I also connected it to the Switch Lite, thus having access to a completely different level of gaming experience... In fact, I can connect a Joypad and recharge the console while playing by placing the Switch on a support. Unfortunately, no, it is not possible to connect it to the TV with HDMI. The Switch Lite does not have coding for video transmission like the basic version but the usability of the console is significantly improved. The only flaw found is the speed of reading the USB 2.0 stick. The iPad struggles a lot to read photo files but we are talking about large sizes (each photo weighs 15MB on average). I cannot know with extreme certainty what the cause is, the Hub or the pen drive which, being a 2.0, has a much slower transfer speed. Maybe with a 3.0 I wouldn't have had this problem. The dimensions are not small but given the many functions it is presumed to be used on a table or in any case on office supports. However, the weight is not excessive and does not strain the USB-C inputs.

column2: Speed and capacity in the jeans pocket
Guys I'm falling in love with USB C hubs!
column3: These devices are fantastic and in fact as soon as my father saw it he wanted one for himself too! This is why I bought another USB C hub! The most convenient port is certainly the HDMI port which, combined with Huawei's emui software, turns a normal smartphone into a real computer! A couple of times I have successfully used it for the DAD by connecting the screen, keyboard, mouse, ethernet cable and smartphone charging cable to the smartphone! With what has just been said I can assure you that these entries work correctly at the same time! Quality that is not found in all hubs according to what I have read!

I bought this wifi adapter for an old desktop computer and it was perfect as it was described. They can be found at lower prices but I bought this one because it had two antennas that seemed more impressive and I thought (in my ignorance) that the coverage was wider. In the package, in addition to the adapter and the antenna, there is an installation CD which allowed me to configure the device very easily and I liked this a lot. Despite the presence of the CD, I believe that with the most modern operating systems it works plug-and-play. To test the operation of the adapter I tried to connect to my router by first configuring a 2.4GHz connection and then 5GHz and they both work well with a normal speed. Satisfied.

The webcam arrived on time and is excellent! The camera is full HD and also has an internal microphone! It has a removable cap to obscure the video. Included in the package is the webcam and the instruction manual! It is also possible to use it with a tripod as it is equipped with the appropriate housing! In summary it is an excellent product!

I was looking for Bluetooth headphones similar to the Apple ones but more ergonomic because the Apple ones keep slipping away from me!!! they hurt when I wear them and they don't escape when I'm walking fast the sound quality is phenomenal fluid and clean far above expectations. I haven't yet tested the quality of the calls so I will change the review later!! Battery life is normal!! For now a product that I can recommend

My nephew was super surprised by its originality in being able to call take photos play everything with a watch. Furthermore, on the main screen you will find in the foreground the numbers of the parents and the SOS to call in case of emergency. The ringing sounds are quite good. Very very elegant, refined and very light. I got it as a gift for my mom. And just comparable with a branded smartwatch at the same things. It simply connects to your phone with its beautiful beautiful app.

column2: Council. It's cheap and works well

It is very convenient and very good value for money instead of paying a lot of money for branded devices that do the same thing and this one works better

A very interesting object. It goes by God as a lamp during the night. My girls usually sleep with some light this is ideal. Easy to use, it also has Bluetooth when you connect it to your phone. Very nice

Beautiful Beautiful. I put this light chain on the balcony among the truly beautiful flowers. It is a very resistant product. I threw water on it and it rained and nothing happened. It works very well. If you want to decorate a balcony or a gazebo I recommend it. And the battery lasts all night

column2: They are garden light bulbs that create atmosphere but DO NOT illuminate like daylight
column3: Purchased because I wanted something that did not have to be connected to the electricity as their position in the garden is not close to the electricity grid (avoiding unnecessary extension cords) and also to avoid unnecessary consumption. To be powered, the row of light bulbs has a battery that is recharged every day thanks to a small photovoltaic panel that I placed in the sun. The light bulbs do not illuminate like daylight (at least only one row) but they create the right very pleasant atmosphere (my girlfriend and I call it a beer atmosphere) which allows you to drink something under the stars giving the right brightness. For example, it is almost impossible to eat them because they are too dim (in fact we turn on two garden light bulbs as reinforcement). They are crepuscular so they turn on (or manually if you want) when the light almost completely goes out and they go out at the first rays of the sun (I I turn them on and off depending on how long I spend in the garden). They have various fixed lighting modes or various intermittent ones (for Christmas the intermittent ones are excellent). I recommend them if you don't want to connect them to the mains and above all if you don't necessarily want daylighting.

column2: Excellent warm and bright lights. I use them in my camper
column3: I purchased this light chain for my van and the length was perfect to cover the internal perimeter. The included solar panel is extremely functional and is equipped with a storage battery that can also be downloaded via USB. The solar panel can be charged separately from the lights which remain mounted inside the van. A solar charge allows autonomy for several hours and for the use I make of them they have never run out of charge. The light, although LED, provides warm and welcoming lighting. The bulbs are beautiful and with a transparent shell which basically makes them more resistant in case of impacts. Recommended product! Really well designed

column2: You will never find better headphones than these!
column3: I bought them mainly because, needing headphones for the gym that wouldn't fall off, reading the reviews, I decided to get them! Now I'll do the pros and cons: Pros:- Very ergonomic and easy to use, installation is quick and easy! The headphones pair easily and there are touch controls on both headphones for changing songs - Battery life is much longer than high value headphones! I was very amazed and when they pair with bluetooth on the phone you can even see the battery life! - They have rubber pads which are essential for people like me who run, use tools and other machinery so they always remain there and thanks to them they act with noise cancellation, lowering external noises - The audio is really good, you can hear the bass very well and they don't bother you even after hours of listening - They can be put back in their case easily without any problem with the magnetic closure without them falling out at any moment! Cons: None! Conclusion: I was very happy because for such a price you won't find better headphones, not even the top of the range ones have headphones that look and feel so high quality without spending a boatload of money! 5/5 stars! Highly approved

I bought this Bluetooth speaker mainly because I wanted to go in the shower with music and be able to relax properly and seeing the reviews I bought it immediately. Now I'll give you the pros and cons: Pros: - It can be attached wherever you want in the shower and it stays there for hours thanks to the attached suction cup - It has LEDs and two modes that switch from one color to another so it also creates the atmosphere - The speaker's battery lasts a very long time (I charged it once and this will be the fifth shower without having recharged it again) - It's waterproof! So you don't have to be afraid of splashes of water - you can hear the bass a lot, therefore formidable quality/price ratio! Cons: None! Conclusion: I'm having a great time with this case and if you don't want to spend a lot but have the quality of a very expensive case that is also waterproof, get it now! 5/5 stars! Highly recommended

Waterproof and with a beautiful white light ideal for illuminating gardens or even the inside of a garage. Very easy to assemble and with the adjustable bracket you can orient it as you wish. I recommend it to everyone because it is very useful and effective for both external and internal use.

The product is certainly of quality. I didn't have much faith in this type of massager but it turned out to be a surprise. It is very simple to use and has different massage modes. Recommended for those with circulation problems or muscle fatigue. The function that allows you to heat both legs is very useful for those who suffer from cramps and joint pain. The only note is the price but the quality is definitely there.

I bought the balloons for a birthday. The quality of the material is good and the balloons are much larger than they look. Inside there are also numerous balloons with two-color confetti and a ribbon to tie them. Recommended for parties.

The only negative note is the strap for carrying the bag over the shoulder, certainly the backpack version would have been more comfortable. Overall good product.

A product that exceeded my expectations. Easy to assemble and above all convenient for shampoo and more. The hand shower is very comfortable with three different water jets. Furthermore, you can easily replace the hand shower with a customized one. The only negative note is the slightly high price.

For Puzzle enthusiasts it is certainly a different product than usual. The pieces are completely customized and the quality of the wood is very good. The only flaw to point out is that the A5 format is small. In all cases I recommend for gifts or for your own use.

I purchased this epilator a little skeptically to replace the one I purchased a few years ago. The price makes you think that it is not an excellent quality epilator but in reality it does its job perfectly. The light pulses are automatic when the emulator is in contact with the skin and it is possible to adjust it to 9 different intensities. We know that pulsed light (and laser which however cannot be done at home) is the future of hair removal but the prices are exorbitant... with this device it is possible to have EXCELLENT results even at home!

These socks are great. In autumn/winter I have always had the problem (which seems silly but is really annoying) of having very cold toes. These socks were my turning point, they warm up immediately and immediately give a very pleasant sensation of warmth that lasts over time. I cannot give my opinion regarding other activities that can be carried out with them (such as walking in the mountains) because I do not use them for this.

Very nice gadget. I'm using it to place the phone next to the PC and watch TV series while working at the desk. Not yet tested but extremely useful is the option to take the photo remotely via an included remote control.

Product arrived in two days packaged in a small box, excellent for storing the lights after use. The box includes: - a 12 meter cable with lights (warm white colour) with 3 meters of cable and power socket (shuko model) - a remote control already equipped with a battery to turn the lights on/off, change their intensity or change type of light (8 different modes) I used them for the Christmas tree but they are also great for decorating outdoors. Excellent value for money. Recommended product.

Excellent product as described, the touch works very well, the audio is impeccable, they can also be heard from far away compared to others that as soon as you move away a little you disconnect the case is small and therefore they are very comfortable to take everywhere and the charging is super fast the battery life is exceptional I recommend them
Excellent product as described, it holds very well between the air conditioning vents and the phone also remains firmly in place

I didn't think I had made such a useful purchase. Everything you could want from an object like this. Small and compact, it features three USB ports, one of which is 3.0, and a USB-C micro SD memory card port. Very high quality of materials combined with a lightweight product. Simply connect it to your PC to increase the number of inputs. Recommended

I didn't expect a product with such a high quantity. I tried other cell phone holders but none of them held up to the windshield but this one is perfect. The materials are resistant and the grip of the suction cup allows perfect stability. In addition to the support with the suction cup there is a smaller support that attaches to the air vent and an adhesive disc on which to attach the fan. Everything perfect recommended.

Congratulations excellent headset starting from the packaging excellent materials and beautiful to look at as regards the headset comfortable to wear excellent sound quality and in particular for the listener you can leave the smartphone even to a beautiful distance and have the same quality of listening and reception from others. Furthermore, the charging system is really fast and convenient. A great product

An excellent product, material that is decidedly good and pleasant to the touch, you can see that it is of good construction, especially the cable input for charging via USB, which gives a real sense of attention to the construction of the product. It's not noisy at all, I tried activating it at various distances and it works great. It is waterproof and therefore easy to wash, a truly good product.

Excellent garden lights to place on the terrace or on an external open space to create a sweet, warm and welcoming atmosphere. I will put them on the terrace when I have some parties. Each bulb emits 2 W and gives off a discreet light, better if placed close together and not too far away and distracting. I would buy another row because they are really beautiful. The package also includes an instruction booklet and two spare bulbs.

Seems to work. We were full of pigeons, even the neighbors now don't seem to lean on our house anymore and they no longer make droppings on the sidewalk and on the front door. It rained the other day and it still seems to work so it's really waterproof.
Excellent outdoor spotlight easy to install with a good detection sensor. A place illuminated by the sun's rays is advisable. Excellent purchase with zero impact.

Excellent protective film to protect the screen of the Xiaomi 10T. The advice is to be very precise when inserting the film as just one smudge could ruin the whole thing. I can't tell you how protective it is because the phone hasn't been dropped yet due to the necessary spells. However, it seems to resist scratches well. Recommended.

The Bluetooth speaker is waterproof, you can use it wherever you want. I personally use it when I do outdoor training where I need the test track. Very easy to connect to your phone. The value for money is very good. The sound comes out quite clean then it is clear that you have to relate to reality and the price spent. Amazon impeccable throughout the entire process.

Support for photographic backdrops of excellent workmanship. The product is light but at the same time robust. Assembly is easy and the possibility of adjusting the width of the support thanks to the horizontal rod made up of 4 modules is very useful. Everything is supplied in a practical transport bag. Three solid color backdrops (white, black, green) are also included. Recommended for the excellent quality-price ratio. Amazon, as always, does not deny itself.
Excellent men's hair clipper, easy to use and with a very precise and thin cut. The charge lasts approximately one hour and the duration in use is more or less similar.

column2: Excellent and at a good price
column3: Bought to connect PS1 and PS2 to a Samsung SmartTV. Excellent device, easy to use and with excellent performance. I didn't find any lag or flickering and the sound comes out clean. Also a positive note is that the USB cable for power supply is provided and is not included by other retailers. Recommended.

Quality product: the magnet is strong enough to withstand any jolts in the car and thanks to the stickers to be applied to the back of the mobile phone the support is even more stable. A free perfume to insert inside which does not saturate the car as often happens with similar products. Fair price. Recommended.

Excellent for shooting in the dark, excellent front lighting with three light levels and good visibility of the rear light with two lighting sequences. Used for shift work, I feel very comfortable both early in the morning and late at night. Then the powerbank with the excellent cell phone holder. Long battery life. Durable material.
Working product I have already tried to use it only once and already small results can be seen then in the box there is really a lot of liquid so it also lasts a long time I recommend it to everyone.

Purchased for the children's bedroom. Arrived as expected by the seller, collected from the Amazon box under the house in an anonymous and intact package, the projector with various functions including one with a red spiral and one that projects stars all around, different background modes, a port for a micro SD from which you can it can listen to our favorite music, it is equipped with a remote control with a modern and minimalist design, practical and intuitive, well made, the children are happy with it and therefore I recommend it.

Purchased on the advice of a friend. Arrived as expected in anonymous and intact packaging, collected in the Amazon box near my house. Small and light, just connect it to an electrical socket and you're done. I'm tormented by mosquitoes and I was fed up with all the various alternatives such as plates and various stoves, the various mosquito traps which are also unpleasant as well as poisonous. With this I eliminated the problem, really convenient. and ecological without any type of substance. I recommend it to everyone.

Arrived on time, anonymous and intact box, collected from the Amazon box under my house. The shower head is adjustable in three different modes. Assembly is simple. Included in the package are all the reductions that can be used for its installation. Practical and lightweight. Well made. I recommend it.
Very resistant nylon cable for Apple Watch magnet with excellent hold, excellent charging speed, nothing to envy of the original. Excellent quality/price ratio

Very nice, comfortable and elegant Milanese mesh style strap. The magnetic closure is firm and easy to take off and put back on and has not caused any type of irritation even after sweating. I recommend it for the excellent quality/price ratio.

I was amazed at how this scale can really measure all these parameters relating to our weight. Furthermore, via the app it is possible not only to monitor the weight day by day but also to understand whether the various parameters are normal or not. Excellent value for money, I recommend purchasing.
Excellent product tested for a few weeks before writing the review. I was satisfied with these headphones. They connect immediately and I must admit that the sound is really not bad at a super price!

Wow finally a worthy product! Excellent well made material protects children from sticking their fingers in it so safe. It does its job optimally, I hung it in mid-air and it is perfect. Also useful in the garden for a mosquito-free barbecue!!

The device is excellent not only for relieving neck pain but can also be used to massage the soles of the feet, the lumbar area and the belly! It can be used both at home and in the car thanks to the double socket and in addition to massaging it also heats up, thus providing double relief. The design is minimal and very elegant. It also features a life-saving type system whereby when it heats up too much it switches itself off to avoid overheating. At this price it was a great deal considering the money you save compared to a shatzu massage. Excellent!
The base is perfect purchased for the PS5 joypads but can also be used to charge mobile phones that have the same input. Essential design but excellent result.

Very useful three feet for holding cell phones and sports cameras, excellent both for taking photos and for holding the cell phone still to take videos. Control with the wireless remote control works perfectly and is useful for those who don't have anyone to take the photo or even for taking tourist selfies. Very resistant and good quality materials

The rotating brush has three structured heads for cleaning different surfaces such as hobs, kitchen floors, shower floors, sinks, tiles. It is easily recharged via a USB socket and assembly is very easy and intuitive. Very convenient for cleaning those encrusted surfaces without effort and without the use of specific products. Excellent for cleaning corners where it is generally difficult to reach. Not bulky and comes with a cardboard suitcase box useful for its storage

column2: Colored projections even from a distance
column3: The idea of a light projector is very cute and nice. After purchasing the white noise machine, this one of the lights was necessary. We didn't regret it at all. Equipped with different colors of lights, you can also insert a melody and with the practical remote control you can also control it remotely. Rechargeable with a USB socket, we gave it as a gift to the son of friends so he can sleep soundly. Highly recommended

In the package there are 4 markers, two in light tones and two in dark tones. Personally I have them. Dark brown eyebrows and I can use both darker tones. My cousin who has blonde/red tones will use the lighter ones. The marker perfectly covers all the areas where I have gaps. Very easy to use and lasts all day without smudging.

The device is very beautiful. It is small in size and not cluttered. It has three different types of sounds: nature, white music, lullaby. In total there are 16 melodies split between the three sections. Adjustable volume. The color of the light can also be chosen by scrolling through all those available. Beautiful melodies for both children and adults. Highly recommended.

column2: Practical and easy to use product
column3: The product arrived early, I expected it to be bigger but the packaging is small and easy to handle, you can easily carry it in your suitcase. Luckily the product can be recharged with USB so you save a lot compared to those powered by batteries. You must pay attention to the positioning of the electrodes but it is all well explained in the instructions included in the package.
